wiki.content: In this song Madonna admonishes a former partner for taking up with someone new. Q magazine May 2008 asked Madonna about the song's hook. The international superstar replied: That's actually Pharrell's (Williams, one of Candy Shop's producers) line. I agreed to it. That's my follow-up to Gloria Gaynor's 'I Will Survive.'
